Discover the districts of the 5th arrondissement

Immerse yourself in the unique atmosphere of each district of Paris's 5th arrondissement. Each area has its distinct lifestyle and characteristics. Whether you're looking for cultural excitement or the serenity of historic spaces, our apartments will meet your aspirations.

Jardin des Plantes

The Jardin des Plantes is a magnificent botanical garden with tranquillity and natural beauty. The area around the garden is perfect for those looking for a flat in a peaceful setting yet close to the lively centre of the 5th arrondissement.

Monge - Jussieu

Discover the charm of the 5th arrondissement with our rental offers in Monge -- Jussieu , a historic district combining culture and conviviality that is perfect for Parisian life.

Saint-Victor

The Saint-Victor district, with its historic streets and tranquil atmosphere, offers a unique blend of culture, history and modern life. It's a perfect choice for those seeking a quieter residential experience while remaining connected to the hustle and bustle of the Latin Quarter. Experience exclusivity in the 5th arrondissement: our apartments for rent in Saint-Victor offer elegance and history in the heart of Paris.

Mouffetard

The Mouffetard district, known for its picturesque market and charming alleyways, is whole of life. Its many cafés, restaurants and boutiques make it a lively and friendly neighbourhood, ideal for an authentic Parisian experience.

Sorbonne - Latin Quarter

Enjoy a vibrant and historic setting in Paris by exploring our apartments for rent in the Sorbonne -- Quartier Latin - a vibrant neighbourhood ideal for authentic Parisian living.

Val de Grâce

Immerse yourself in the peaceful atmosphere and rich history of Val de Grâce with our selected apartment rentals - a haven of peace in the heart of the 5th arrondissement.
